high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Pick up the potato in the sink.
Step to the right to face the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and step forward to face the kitchen table.
Place the potato on the kitchen table.

Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a right and go to the white table.
Put the potato on the table in front of the egg.
